txt.en: Play to level 2 during our 15th Anniversary Celebration
<rgb=#00e4ff>Receive Collector's Edition Expansion Pack gifts for logging in and reaching level 2 during our 15th Anniversary.</rgb>
<rgb=#00e4ff>Received Expansion Pack Collector's Edition gifts for logging in during our 15th Anniversary.</rgb>

You have received Mordor, Minas Morgul, and War of Three Peaks Expansion Collector's Editions as a gift for logging in during our 15th Anniversary Celebration and adventuring to at least level 2. If not previously owned, the expansion content has now been unlocked for your account. If not previously owned, Collector's Edition items will deliver at your next character login.
